    public interface IHasAttributes
    Interface representing any object that has attributes.

    An attribute consists of a String name and an Object value. A given attribute only has a single value at any given time. In other words, multivalued attributes are not supported.

    Optionally, an implementation can support firing events when an attribute changes.
